{{main|1988年第一号热带低气压}}
本季的第一个热带低气压于5月30日在西北加勒比海形成。系统北上朝[[古巴|古巴]]逼近，这一过程中遭遇的外部环境不利于其发展，飞入其中的一架[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]][[侦察机|侦察机]]也无法找到明确的环流中心<ref name="ap0601am">{{cite news | title = Forecasters Watching Depression | work = Domestic News | agency = Associated Press | date = 1988-06-01}}</ref>。低气压强度一直很弱，于6月2日在[[佛罗里达海峡|佛罗里达海峡]]退化成一片开放式[[低压槽|低压槽]]<ref name="TDs1988" />。

低气压及其前身一共给古巴带來高达1025毫米的降水，其中包括一天时间里达到的867毫米<ref name="CUBARAIN">{{cite web | author = Instituto Nacional de Recursos Hidráulicos | year = 2003 | title = Lluvias intensas observadas y grandes inundaciones reportadas | accessdate = 2007-02-10 | url = http://www.hidro.cu/hidrologia1.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131105222344/http://www.hidro.cu/hidrologia1.htm | archivedate = 2013-11-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。受降水影响最为严重的是[[西恩富戈斯省|西恩富戈斯省]]，另外[[比亚克拉拉省|比亚克拉拉省]]、[[圣斯皮里图斯省|圣斯皮里图斯省]]、[[谢戈德阿维拉省|谢戈德阿维拉省]]和[[卡马圭省|卡马圭省]]也受到一定程度的影响<ref name="CUBARAIN" />。[[卡马圭|卡马圭]]市的一场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]摧毁多幢建筑物和5架[[苏联|苏联]]飞机<ref name="ap0602am">{{cite news | title = Storm Kills 14, Six Missing in Cuba | work = International News | agency = Associated Press | date = 1988-06-02}}</ref>。面对洪灾，政府派出救援人员、[[直升机|直升机]]和水陆两栖车将6.5万生活在低洼地区的居民疏散到地势更高的区域。气旋导致许多地方的电力和通讯中断，该国交通基础设施严重受损，6座桥梁也被摧毁<ref name="ap0602am" />。单卡马圭省就有200套民房被洪水摧毁，另有1000套房屋受到破坏<ref name="ria0608">{{cite news | title = Cuba – Flood | publisher = The Russian Information Agency | date = 1988-06-08}}</ref>。整个古巴有约9万人受灾，数十人受伤<ref name="rwtd1">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-10-09 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/cuba/cuba-heavy-rains-jun-1988-undro-information-report-no-1 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131009023819/http://reliefweb.int/report/cuba/cuba-heavy-rains-jun-1988-undro-information-report-no-1 | title = Cuba – Heavy Rains Jun 1988 UNDRO Information Report No. 1 | accessdate = 2014-06-26 | date = 1988-06-10 | publisher = United Nations Department of Humanitarian Affairs | deadurl = no }}</ref>，共计37人遇难<ref name="CUBARAIN" />，其中有3人是触电身亡<ref name="ap0602am" />。低气压还给[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]带來小雨，其中[[庞帕诺比奇_(佛罗里达州)|庞帕诺比奇]]达到81毫米<ref name="td1rain">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-09-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921083523/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td1of1988.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/td1of1988.html | title = Rainfall Summary for Tropical Depression One | accessdate = 2014-06-26 | author = David Roth | year = 2006 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center }}</ref>。
