本季的第三股热带低气压于8月7日由[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]东南部上空的一片地面[[低气压|低气压]]形成。系统在缓慢朝[[密西西比河|密西西比河]]飘移的过程中逐渐组织起来，很快就拥有足够多的[[对流|对流]]，促使美国国家飓风中心发布第三号热带低气压的初步公告<ref name="beryltcr1">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/beryl/prelim01.gif | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Preliminary Report (Page 1) | accessdate = 2014-06-26 | year = 1988 | format = GIF | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019040812/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/beryl/prelim01.gif | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。8月8日，低气压的表面风速已加快到足以令气象部门向路易斯安那州和佛罗里达州西北狭长地带发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]<ref name="mwr" />。风暴在位于墨西哥湾开放水域上空期间给路易斯安那州、[[密西西比州|密西西比州]]和[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]]带來的持续风速属热带风暴最低标准，阵风时速也达到热带风暴强度<ref name="beryltcr2">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/beryl/prelim02.gif | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Preliminary Report (Page 2) | accessdate = 2014-06-26 | year = 1988 | format = GIF | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019040818/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/beryl/prelim02.gif | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。墨西哥湾中部沿海地区普降暴雨，其中阿拉巴马州[[多芬岛_(阿拉巴马州)|多芬岛]]的降雨量在410毫米以上<ref name="berylrain">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-09-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130922031502/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/beryl1988.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/beryl1988.html | title = Rainfall Summary for Tropical Storm Beryl | accessdate = 2014-06-26 | author = David Roth | year = 2006 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center }}</ref>。

贝丽尔保持着良好的外流结构，其环流于8月9日进入温度较高的水域上空，有利于风暴进一步增强。但由于西北方向有一股冷锋逼近，风暴因此转向进入路易斯安那州东南部<ref name="berylrain" />。次日早上，贝丽尔已在进入该州中南部的[[泰克河口|泰克河口]]（{{lang|en|Bayou Teche}}）上空后降级成热带低气压。系统残留给德克萨斯州东部带來倾盆大雨，部分地区降雨量超过300毫米。这场风暴总体造成的破坏很小，但有导致一人死亡<ref name="beryltcr3">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/beryl/prelim03.gif | title = Tropical Storm Beryl Preliminary Report (Page 3) | accessdate = 2014-06-26 | year = 1988 | format = GIF | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019040829/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/beryl/prelim03.gif | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。
