8月15日，一股强劲的东风波离开非洲西海岸，到8月21日时，东风波北翼已有对流分离并组织成第七号热带低气压<ref name="debbytcr1">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1988 | title = Hurricane Debby Preliminary Report (Page 1) | accessdate = 2014-06-26 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/debby/prelim01.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121021005418/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/debby/prelim01.gif | archivedate = 2012-10-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴沿中大西洋各州上空一片[[副热带高压脊|副热带高压脊]]的南部边缘向西行进，之后的七天里，无论地面还是侦察机都没有发现风暴强化的迹象，因此气象部门认为系统在行经[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]和[[大安的列斯群岛|大安的列斯群岛]]部分地区以及[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]期间都保持在热带低气压强度<ref name="mwr" />。

低气压于8月24日途经[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]以南海域，给该岛部分区域带來超过360毫米降雨量<ref name="chrisrain">{{cite web | author = David Roth | year = 2006 | title = Rainfall Summary for Tropical Storm Chris | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | accessdate = 2014-06-26 | archivedate = 2013-09-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130922030143/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/chris1988.html | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/chris1988.html }}</ref>，造成当地3人遇难<ref name="christcr2">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1988 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Preliminary Report (Page 2) | accessdate = 2014-06-26 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/chris/prelim02.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121013001600/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/chris/prelim02.gif | archivedate = 2012-10-13 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。8月28日，气旋在北上到达佛罗里达州北部近海后升级成热带风暴克里斯，然后在[[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]附近登陆，给该地区带來轻微的风灾和雨害<ref name="christcr2" />。克里斯在减弱成热带低气压的过程中给南卡罗莱纳州带來瓢泼大雨，之后与一片[[冷锋|冷锋]]融合并转变成温带气旋。残留低气压在东部沿海地区加速行进，经过[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]并最终于8月30日消散<ref name="chrisrain" />。强烈的雷暴在南卡罗莱纳州催生出一场龙卷风，导致一人死亡<ref name="christcr1">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1988 | title = Tropical Storm Chris Preliminary Report (Page 1) | accessdate = 2014-06-26 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/chris/prelim01.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193255/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/chris/prelim01.gif | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。
