9月4日，一道云带伴随着一股冷锋一起离开德克萨斯州海岸进入墨西哥湾。云带在海湾中部分裂成两个部分，其中南半部分基本保持静止，而北半部分则发展成一股向东北方向前进的锋面波。南半部分上空的对流有所增加，并围绕云层中心缠绕起来。9月7日，系统有表面环流形成，美国国家飓风中心因此开始发布热带低气压公告。<ref name="florencetcr1">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/florence/prelim01.gif | title = Hurricane Florence Preliminary Report (Page 1) | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | year = 1988 | format = GIF | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019021737/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/florence/prelim01.gif | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

由于逐渐消散锋面槽的影响，低气压向东飘移，并且经飓风猎人侦察机确认已增强成热带风暴，美国国家飓风中心将其命名为“佛罗伦萨”（{{lang|en|Florence}}）<ref name="florencetcr1" />。9月9日，风暴转向北上，并在一片中到上层槽的影响下加速朝墨西哥湾北部移动，于登陆[[密西西比河三角洲|密西西比河三角洲]]数小时前达到飓风强度<ref name="mwr" />。风暴在路易斯安那州东南部上空迅速减弱，并在行经[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]后失去所有深层对流。9月10日，风暴在[[巴吞鲁日_(路易斯安那州)|巴吞鲁日]]附近上空降级为低气压，并于次日在德克萨斯州东北部上空消散<ref name="florencetcr1" />。

系统存在早期给尤卡坦半岛带來中等程度降水<ref name="florencerain">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-09-21 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/florence1988.html | title = Rainfall Summary for Hurricane Florence | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130921194258/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/florence1988.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | author = David Roth | year = 2006 | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center }}</ref>。风暴吹袭路易斯安那州期间，其中心登岸区域偏东方向附近沿海出现中等程度的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]<ref name="florencetcr2">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/florence/prelim02.gif | title = Hurricane Florence Preliminary Report (Page 2) | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | year = 1988 | format = GIF | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019021838/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/florence/prelim02.gif | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。阵风导致超过10万人失去电力供应。阿拉巴马州有一人在试图稳固自己的船只时遇难。降雨导致佛罗里达州西北狭长地带部分河流严重泛滥，该区域之前已经受到暴雨的严重影响，洪水导致[[聖羅薩縣_(佛羅里達州)|聖羅薩縣]]有数十套房屋受损或被毁<ref name="florencetcr3">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/florence/prelim03.gif | title = Hurricane Florence Preliminary Report (Page 3) | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | year = 1988 | format = GIF | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019021833/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/florence/prelim03.gif | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。
