=== 热带风暴艾萨克 ===
{{Infobox Hurricane Small
|Basin=Atl
|Image=Isaac 30 sept 1988 1947Z.jpg
|Track=Isaac 1988 track.png
|Formed=9月28日
|Dissipated=10月1日
|1-min winds=40
|Pressure=1005
}}
9月23日，一股弱扰动天气离开非洲海岸向西行进，进入[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]的低纬度海域，其对流逐渐组织起来并有所增加<ref name="isaactcr1">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/isaac/prelim01.gif | title = Tropical Storm Isaac Preliminary Report (Page 1) | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | year = 1988 | format = GIF | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140322111309/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/isaac/prelim01.gif | archivedate = 2014-03-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。9月29日，系统在[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]东南方向约1400公里洋面发展成第十六号热带低气压。风暴的西向行动路径朝北面略偏2度，这可能是因为其中有新的中心正在形成。9月30日，[[美国空军|空军]]侦察机发现低气压风速已达到热带风暴强度，气象部门因此将其升级为热带风暴并命名为“艾萨克”（{{lang|en|Isaac}}）<ref name="mwr" />。由于存在西向风切变的不利影响，风暴中心无法发展出深层对流。随着艾萨克的逼近，小安的列斯群岛北部收到热带风暴警告<ref name="mwr" />。不过，这场风暴由于风切变的不利影响而只持续很短的时间。10月1日，系统降级成低气压，之后很快就完全消散<ref name="isaactcr1" />。艾萨克的残留之后在东太平洋得到重生，发展成第二十{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压<ref name="tc20ed1103Z">{{cite web | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1988/td20e/tropdisc/tcd1103z.gif | title = Tropical Depression Twenty-E Discussion for 0300 UTC | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | date = 1988-10-11 | format = GIF | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140322120129/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1988/td20e/tropdisc/tcd1103z.gif | archivedate = 2014-03-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

这一天气系统作为热带气旋期间没有对陆地造成显著影响<ref name="prelim2">{{cite web | author = Miles B. Lawrence | date = 1988-10-30 | title = Tropical Storm Isaac Preliminary Report (Page 2) | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024042839/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/isaac/prelim02.gif | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/isaac/prelim02.gif }}</ref>。但是系统残留却给整个[[特立尼达和多巴哥|特立尼达和多巴哥]]带來暴雨，引发洪灾和多场泥石流，造成20人受伤<ref name="upi" />，还令至少30人流离失所<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Saint Petersburg Times | date = 1988-10-04 | title = 2 die as storm lashes islands}}</ref>。莫凡特（{{lang|en|Morvant}}）有两人在山洪暴发期间丧生<ref name="upi">{{cite news | author = Lindsay Mackoon | date = 1988-10-02 | title = Storm wreaks havoc on Trinidad | agency = United Press International}}</ref>，该国还有多条道路和桥梁受损<ref>{{cite web | author = World Loss Report | date = 1988-10-21 | title = Occurrence and reports: Natural Catastrophe}}</ref>。
