10月10日，热带辐合带的一片扰动天气发展成本季第十七号热带低气压，之后两天里系统向西北方向前进并达到热带风暴强度，美国国家飓风中心因此将其命名为“琼”（{{lang|en|Joan}}）<ref name="joantcr7">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1988 | title = Hurricane Joan Preliminary Report (Page 7) | accessdate = 2007-10-10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/joan/prelim07.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120406084340/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/joan/prelim07.gif | archivedate = 2012-04-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。经过小安的列斯群岛南部后，气旋以热带风暴的最低标准强度沿[[南美洲|南美洲]]海岸向西进发，于10月18日穿过[[瓜希拉半岛|瓜希拉半岛]]并在距海岸线仅48公里海域迅速达到飓风标准。10月19日，还在向西飘移的琼增强为大型飓风。接下来风暴的移动路径形成一个紧密的圆，并在这一过程中大幅减弱，但在恢复向西移动后又得到快速强化<ref name="joantcr2">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1988 | title = Hurricane Joan Preliminary Report (Page 2) | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/joan/prelim02.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120406084347/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/joan/prelim02.gif | archivedate = 2012-04-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。10月22日，系统达到最高强度，之后不久便以四级飓风标准从[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]][[布卢菲尔兹|布卢菲尔兹]]附近登陆。当时创下位置最南面的四级飓风纪录，直到[[2004年大西洋飓风季|2004年]]才被[[飓风伊万|飓风伊万]][[飓风伊万的气象历史|超越]]<ref name="IvanTCR">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 2005 | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Hurricane Ivan | accessdate = 2007-10-10 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2004ivan.shtml? | archivedate = 2013-04-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130403015719/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2004ivan.shtml }}</ref>。琼在穿越尼加拉瓜后仍然保持着良好的组织结构，并在进入东太平洋后获重新指定成热带风暴米利安，之后逐渐减弱，于11月2日消散<ref name=NHCMiriamp2>{{cite report | author = Dr. Harold P. Gerrish | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120406084436/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1988-prelim/miriam/prelim02.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/epacific/ep1988-prelim/miriam/prelim02.gif | title = Tropical Storm Miriam Preliminary Report (Page 2) | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | archivedate = 2012-04-06 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。

琼共计夺走216人的生命，其中148人来自尼加拉瓜<ref name="joantcr3">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1988 | title = Hurricane Joan Preliminary Report (Page 3) | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/joan/prelim03.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120406084457/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/joan/prelim03.gif | archivedate = 2012-04-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。这场飓风共计造成20亿美元（1988年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|2000000000|1988}}}}美元）的损失，其中单尼加拉瓜就占了一半。风暴还给加勒比地区最南部沿线多个国家带來暴雨和泥石流<ref name="joantcr2" />，其沿南美洲北部海岸的行进路径对于大西洋飓风来说非常罕见<ref name="joantcr1">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1988 | title = Hurricane Joan Preliminary Report (Page 1) | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/joan/prelim01.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120406084356/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/joan/prelim01.gif | archivedate = 2012-04-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。此外，琼还是继1978年的[[飓风葛丽泰-奥利维亚|飓风葛丽泰]]以来第一个穿过大西洋盆地的热带气旋<ref name="noaafaqe">{{cite web | author = NOAA | year = 2007 | title = FAQ Part E: Tropical Cyclone Records (Page 1) | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqE.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140325075113/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/tcfaqE.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-03-25 }}</ref>。
