{{Main|热带风暴基斯}}
本季最后一场风暴于11月17日由[[海地|海地]]以南的一股东风波形成。系统向西行经加勒比海，于11月20日达到热带风暴强度标准并因此获命名为“基斯”（{{lang|en|Keith}}）。风暴迅速强化并达到风速每小时110公里的最高强度，然后于11月21日登陆尤卡坦半岛东北部。在一片上层低压槽的影响下，气旋转向东北，并因上层风切变和更为寒冷干燥空气的不利影响减弱到热带风暴的最低强度标准，这对11月的热带气旋来说较为常见<ref name="mwr" /><ref name="keithtcr1">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1988 | title = Tropical Storm Keith Preliminary Report (Page 1) | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/keith/prelim01.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019040716/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/keith/prelim01.gif | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-06-27 }}</ref>。基斯在墨西哥湾东南部再度增强，于11月23日从佛罗里达州[[萨拉索塔_(佛罗里达州)|萨拉索塔]]附近登陆。行经该州后，风暴于11月24日在百慕大附近转变成温带气旋，而且在大西洋上空发展成一个强烈的温带天气系统，持续风速达到飓风强度的最低标准<ref name="mwr" /><ref name="keithtcr2">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1988 | title = Tropical Storm Keith Preliminary Report (Page 2) | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | archivedate = 2013-12-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131217203544/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/keith/prelim02.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/keith/prelim02.gif }}</ref>。

基斯存在早期就给[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]、牙买加和古巴带來中到大雨<ref name="ap1120">{{cite news | author = Patrick Reyna | date = 1988-11-20 | title = Late-Season Storm Forms; Cuba, Florida Likely Targets | agency = Associated Press}}</ref><ref name="ap1122">{{cite news | author = Brian Murphy | date = 1988-11-22 | title = Storm Keith Hovers In Gulf, Could Strike Florida | agency = Associated Press}}</ref><ref name="keithtcr3">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1988 | title = Tropical Storm Keith Preliminary Report (Page 3) | accessdate = 2014-06-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019040740/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/keith/prelim03.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1988-prelim/keith/prelim03.gif | date = 2012-10-19 | archivedate = 2012-10-19 }}</ref>。[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]在两个月前受到[[飓风吉伯特|飓风吉伯特]]的重创尚未完全恢复，幸而在这场风暴中所受破坏很小<ref name="gam1122">{{cite news | author = ''The Globe and Mail (Canada)'' | date = 1988-11-22 | title = Tropical storm Keith hits Yucatan, western Cuba}}</ref>。气旋给佛罗里达州中部带來中等程度降水，还有强烈的风暴潮和阵风<ref name="mwr" />，总体受到破坏的地区范围很广，但程度较轻，总计经济损失约为730万美元（1988年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|7300000|1988}}}}美元）<ref name="keithtcr3" /><ref name="damtotpi">{{cite news | author = Thomas C. Tobin | date = 1988-12-07 | title = Damage from Keith won't qualify for aid | publisher = Saint Petersburg Times}}</ref>。沿海地区受到的破坏主要源于风暴潮和海滩侵蚀，更为内陆的地区则出现洪灾，还有树木倒塌，供电线路中断，幸而没有出现人员丧生<ref name="keithtcr3" />。
